content.rendered:
Engineered to provide the highest strength, reliability & safety. The Outback Armour 10T Rated Snatch Block snatch block has been independently tested at over 15 tonnes and is rated by a factor of 1.5:1

The Outback Armour 10T rated snatch block features a cnc machined pully wheel, accepts up to 25mm bow shackle pin, has a grease nipple and an internal spiral cut brass bush for grease distribution.

Specifications Details
Rating: 10T WLL
Rating Factor: 1.5:1 WLL tested
Side Plates: pressed cold rolled steel
Pulley: CNC machined solid steel (98mm)
Max. Cable: 9.5mm steel or plasma/dyneema

excerpt.rendered: Rated hardware for the safety of you and your vehicle!
